        "timestamp": "2020-06-19 20:10:47.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 5: Code-Review-1\n\n(4 comments)\n\nAlgorithm looks sound to me, just need to fix a few things.\n\nPerhaps in a future JIRA we can rework this to use non-blocking I/O in the web requests, which would eliminate the need for the executor service.  However, that would require some rework to split the fetchXxx() method into makeRequest() and processResponse() pieces, so I'm good with this for now.",
